KARMA: The Dark World's FREE Filter Mode Update is OUT NOW on PlayStation 5.

Experience the mind bending cinematic world of KARMA with a fresh layer of immersion to the dystopian mind-bending narrative by letting players alter how they see the world with six visual filters: 

8MM film 
Fisheye 
Dreamcore 
Old Film 
Black and White 
Low Saturation 

Are you ready to step back into the darkness and uncover the secrets that lurk in the shadows of your mind?
